de.fub.agg2graph.agg

Class AggNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fub.agg2graph.structs.AbstractLocation
      • de.fub.agg2graph.structs.GPSPoint
        • de.fub.agg2graph.agg.AggNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Hideable, ILocation
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ShallowAggNode

    public class AggNode
extends GPSPoint
    Node in the aggregation. A node can have multiple incoming and outgoing AggConnections linking other AggNodes. It is capable of saving the intersection information (how many tracks from which input to which output).
    Author:
    Johannes Mitlmeier
